TextEng: Okay, me go now, yuh?
Out of my way, money-grubber.
Nevermind.
Me have questions, you answer, yuh?
Text: 나 질문 있어, 너 대답해, 응?

TextEng: Urgh, you in me way...
Text: 으, 너 내 길 막고 있어...

TextEng: Uh, me go now.
I don't like thinking about snapping your neck but that won't stop me...
Text: 네 목을 부러뜨릴 생각은 싫지만 그래도 막지는 않을 거야...

TextEng: No, you tell! You tell or me crush you!
Text: 아니, 너 말해! 너 말하지 않으면 나 너 으깨!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> If you're a sword for hire, where else have you served?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 검을 팔고 다니는 사람이라면, 어디서 복무했어요?

TextEng: You mercenary. Me pay you, you follow, yuh?
Text: 너 용병이야. 나 돈 줘, 너 따라와, 응?

TextEng: Me want healer priest.
Thanks, that's everything.
Me tree-friend. Der other tree-friends here? Druids an' Rangers?
Text: 나 자연의 친구야. 여기 다른 자연의 친구 있어? 드루이드랑 순찰자?

TextEng: Me want place to sleep and drink.
Text: 나 자고 술 마실 곳 원해.

TextEng: What type store around here?
Any other towns nearby?
Could you answer a few questions for me?
Text: 질문 몇 가지 대답해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Does Port Llast have a ranger or druid I could speak with?
Text: 라스트 항구에 순찰자나 드루이드가 있나요? 대화하고 싶은데요.

TextEng: Where can I find an inn?
You're a mercenary. That mean you're for hire?
Know where I can find a priest?
What kind of stores do you have around here?
Are there any other towns in the region?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> What can you tell me about Luskan?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 러스칸에 대해 뭘 알려줄 수 있어요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Luskan? What that like?
I need some directions.
Me need directions.
I'm looking for some people.
Me look for certain kind of people.
Text: 나 특정 종류 사람들 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Could you answer some other questions?
Text: 다른 질문들에 대답해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: You answer other stuff?
